<seg id=1> Dinosaur fossils found in Henan Xixia. </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News agency, Zhengzhou, April 23rd, by Yamin Lui- Recently some specialists and scholars found lots of Dinosaur fossils in Henan Xixia county in the village of Yangcheng. </seg>
<seg id=3> This is an important find following last year's discovery of a deposit containing many very precious and rare dinosaur bones. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> The reporter got this news from the Henan Archeological Research Institution. in early April of this year the researchers found several hundred pieces of dinosaur bones which included vertebrae and toe bones in the area between Henan Xixia county village of Yangcheng and Hutou Mountain. </seg>
<seg id=5> Because the fossils had been exposed to the weather on the surface for so long, most of them are broken in pieces. </seg>
<seg id=6> From the age of the rocks the bones were found in, they should belong to the Cretaceous Period. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> According to the researchers predictions they expect to find more vertebrae and other animal bones in this area. </seg>
<seg id=8> They consider Xixia valley very unique in that there have been many rare fossil dinosaur eggs found, and even more unusual is to find both egg fossils and fossils from adult dinosaurs together. </seg>
<seg id=9> This discovery holds very important meanings for further researches into the areas: such as the locations where dinosaurs may have lived in the Xixia area.  Further study of dinosaurs living behavior and methods of reproduction.  Reconstructing the environment when dinosaurs lived.  To find out principles of how the earth's environment has changed. </seg>
<seg id=10> The discovery of the dinosaur fossils also provides important hints for where researchers should look for additional fossils and how these bones fossils were buried. </seg>
</p>
